title: Polar Bear with Plastic
description: A polar bear is swimming in water, holding a piece of plastic in its mouth along with a fish. The bear's fur is white and wet, and it appears to be in a natural habitat, highlighting the impact of pollution on wildlife.

title: Forest After a Fire
description: A landscape showing a forest area with many dead trees, likely the aftermath of a wildfire. The sky is bright blue with a few clouds, and there is some green vegetation visible on the ground, indicating regrowth.

title: Bird on a Branch
description: A bird perched on a branch in front of a large, intricate nest made of twigs and leaves. The background features a clear blue sky and green foliage, suggesting a vibrant natural setting.
